blocks.heading: Hi, we’re Acme. We make tools like Super™ and Track® that are used by thousands of teams worldwide.
blocks.text: We’re serious about creating amazing products, practices, open work, accessibility, and inclusivity. And in all that we strive to embed a good amount of fun. We’re rooted in the open source community and deeply care about giving back.

blocks.heading: Our leadership
blocks.subhead: At the end of the day customer centric, so circle back translating our vision of having a market leading platform into the weeds let's schedule a standup during the sprint to review our KPIs.

blocks.heading: Company culture comes in many shapes and forms, but we particularly pride ourselves on:

content.heading: Be excellent to each other
content.text: We’re open, kind, and honest. We don’t play games, and we’re here to be our best selves.

content.heading: Care about our team
content.text: Bottleneck mice table the discussion offline

content.heading: Push the limits
content.text: We love breaking new grounds, and revel in unknowns. Always ask “why not?”

content.heading: Live our values
content.text: We live and breathe integrity, empathy, and quality. Always and in everything we do.

content.heading: Love our users
content.text: We listen to the user and also hear their unstated needs.
